import React from 'react';
import { Avatar, Box, Grid, Typography, makeStyles } from '@mui/material';

const useStyles = makeStyles({
   container: {
      backgroundColor: "rgba(0, 145, 136, 0.8)",
      paddingTop: "10%",
      paddingLeft: "10%",
      paddingRight: "10%",
   },
   firstText: {
      fontFamily: "Noto Sans",
      fontWeight: 500,
      fontSize: "32px",
   },
   secondText: {
      fontFamily: "Noto Sans",
      fontWeight: 800,
      fontSize: "62px",
      textAlign: "end"
   },
   thirdText: {
      fontFamily: "Noto Sans",
      fontWeight: 700,
      fontSize: "38px",
      textAlign: "end"
   },
})

export const PresentationPage = () => {
   const classes = useStyles();

   return (
      <Box className={classes.container}>
         <Grid container direction="column">
            <Grid item>
               <Grid container direction="row">
                  <Grid item>
                     <Typography className={classes.firstText}>
                        Olá! Eu sou Bianca Sakaniwa, uma
                     </Typography>
                  </Grid>
                  <Grid item>
                     <Avatar src="" variant="circular" />
                  </Grid>
               </Grid>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item sx={{ paddingTop: "10%" }}>
               <Typography className={classes.secondText}>
                  Desenvolvedora de Software Fullstack
               </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
               <Typography className={classes.thirdText}>
                  Com ênfase em front-end
               </Typography>
            </Grid>
         </Grid>
      </Box>
   )
}
